# Netlify / Cloudflare Pages redirects.
# (Vercel: use vercel.json instead.)
#
# Single-page site, no SPA routing needed. We only need:
#  - HTTPS enforcement (auto on Netlify/CF)
#  - Apex → www canonicalization (or vice-versa — pick one)
#
# Decide AT DEPLOY TIME whether your canonical is the apex or www. Uncomment
# whichever one of the two lines below matches your choice, leave the other
# commented. Wrong choice = SEO + share-link mess.

# Option A: canonical = apex (https://yourdomain.com) — most common
# https://www.yourdomain.com/*    https://yourdomain.com/:splat   301!

# Option B: canonical = www (https://www.yourdomain.com)
# https://yourdomain.com/*        https://www.yourdomain.com/:splat   301!
